    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1379560/extras/59a915cd0f84eba44ae02481212443cb.poster.avif?t=1734979722\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1379560/extras/59a915cd0f84eba44ae02481212443cb.webm?t=1734979722\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1379560/extras/59a915cd0f84eba44ae02481212443cb.mp4?t=1734979722\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >9个可玩的角色</h2>扮演你最喜爱的《史帝芬宇宙》角色，包括史帝芬、石榴石、珍珠、紫水晶、青金石和铋晶！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >打造专属队伍</h2>选择让哪些宝石人加入你的队伍，解锁超强新能力，装备替换服装，还可更改战斗队形获取对战优势。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >两名新宝石人</h2>与Rebecca Sugar协力打造的两名宝石人将手持棱柱登场，奋力对抗他们吧。他们是谁，又在密谋什么？<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >合体时间！</h2>通过组队实现超强连击，并能与宝石人合体！通过合体来扮演烟水晶、太阳石和彩红水晶2.0！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >原创配音</h2>《绽放光芒》内含与Rebecca Sugar共同创作的原创故事，还有来自《小卷毛》幕后阵容和特邀演员Christine Baranski倾情配音。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1379560/extras/bffc5a76c9ebe38f516f18f52a3b49e7.avif?t=1734979722\" width=600 height=388 /></span>",
